                    <h2 class="text-base font-semibold tracking-wider text-cyan-600 uppercase">FEATURES</h2>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
                        Everything you need to create a web-app
                    </p>
                    <p class="mt-5 max-w-prose mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500">
                        fritz2 is lightweight, reactive and easy to learn
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-12">
